口述 | 24小时登上100多架航班，我在飞机上对重点地区旅客进行排查。
Oral & # 124; # 124; & # 45; boarded more than 100 flights in a 24-hour flight, where I screened passengers in key areas.
孙明沁 应　琛。
Sun Ming Ying Chen.
